Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.64,0:02:54.69,OPch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}记忆如花瓣般衰败消散
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.86,0:03:06.37,OPch,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,150)}触碰的瞬间 破碎散落
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.96,0:03:14.34,OPch,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,150)}带我走吧!
